{"type":"message","id":"527487dc","parentId":"9f1d4573","timestamp":"2026-03-05T02:01:59.815Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户确认我理解了需求，让我开始工作完成升级。根据之前分析的文章，我需要实现 Agent Swarm 编排系统。\n\n让我规划一下需要做什么：\n\n1. **创建 Agent 任务跟踪系统**\n   - `.clawdbot/active-tasks.json` - 跟踪进行中的任务\n   - `.clawdbot/completed-tasks/` - 已完成的任务\n\n2. **创建监控脚本**\n   - `check-agents.sh` - 定时检查Agent状态\n   - 检查tmux会话、PR状态、CI结果\n\n3. **创建 Prompt 生成模板**\n   - 标准化的prompt结构\n\n4. **创建工作流自动化脚本**\n   - spawn-agent.sh - 启动Agent\n   - handle-failure.sh - 处理失败\n\n5. **更新 Memory 系统**\n   - 记录成功/失败的prompt模式\n   - 积累经验\n\n让我开始实现这些组件。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"开始实现 Agent Swarm 编排系统升级！"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-78c8c60900bf4358ac7133face1806c7","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mkdir -p ~/.openclaw/workspace-tech-lead/.clawdbot/{scripts,templates,logs,completed-tasks}"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-db45ace7d7f44fa195b11988a949299f","name":"write","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/lihzz/.openclaw/workspace-tech-lead/.clawdbot/active-tasks.json","content":"{\n  \"version\": \"1.0\",\n  \"description\": \"Agent Swarm 任务跟踪系统 - Elvis 架构实现\",\n  \"tasks\": [],\n  \"metadata\": {\n    \"lastUpdated\": \"2026-03-05T10:01:00+08:00\",\n    \"activeCount\": 0,\n    \"completedToday\": 0\n  }\n}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"alibaba","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":26173,"output":565,"cacheRead":1272,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":28010,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772676106263}}
