{"type":"message","id":"fa7a1dac","parentId":"8d343bce","timestamp":"2026-03-05T02:28:31.186Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user sent \"1\" - this seems like a continuation or acknowledgment. Let me continue setting up the Agent Swarm system. I should complete the setup by:\n\n1. Making the scripts executable\n2. Creating the directory structure for projects\n3. Writing a quick reference guide\n4. Setting up cron jobs for monitoring\n5. Creating an initial memory file for Alex\n\nLet me continue with the setup.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"继续完成系统设置："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-5087fe8c99184e1ab9fe52458001a226","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"chmod +x ~/.openclaw/workspace-tech-lead/.clawdbot/scripts/*.sh && ls -la ~/.openclaw/workspace-tech-lead/.clawdbot/scripts/"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-e2bb677db10342319f5ff5f1431fc097","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# Agent Swarm 系统快速参考\n\n## 📁 目录结构\n\n```\n.clawdbot/\n├── active-tasks.json        # 活跃任务队列\n├── scripts/\n│   ├── spawn-agent.sh       # Agent生成器\n│   ├── check-agents.sh      # 监控脚本\n│   ├── check-dod.sh         # DoD检查\n│   ├── select-agent.sh      # Agent选择器\n│   ├── ralph-loop.sh        # 智能失败处理\n│   └── discover-work.sh     # 主动工作发现\n├── templates/\n│   ├── feature-development.md\n│   └── bugfix.md\n├── memory/\n│   ├── prompt-patterns.json    # Prompt模式库\n│   └── agent-performance.json  # Agent性能统计\n├── logs/                       # 日志目录\n└── completed-tasks/            # 已完成任务归档\n```\n\n## 🚀 常用命令\n\n### 生成编码Agent\n```bash\n# 后端功能\n./.clawdbot/scripts/spawn-agent.sh backend \"实现用户登录\" ~/projects/myapp myapp\n\n# 前端功能\n./.clawdbot/scripts/spawn-agent.sh frontend \"登录页面UI\" ~/projects/myapp myapp \"\" \"\" \"\" true\n\n# Bug修复\n./.clawdbot/scripts/spawn-agent.sh bugfix \"修复登录超时\" ~/projects/myapp myapp\n```\n\n### 监控Agent状态\n```bash\n# 检查所有Agent\n./.clawdbot/scripts/check-agents.sh\n\n# 查看活跃任务\ncat .clawdbot/active-tasks.json | jq '.tasks[] | {id, status, agent}'\n\n# 附加到Agent会话\ntmux attach -t <session-name>\n```\n\n### 检查DoD\n```bash\n# 完整检查\n./.clawdbot/scripts/check-dod.sh feat/templates owner/repo true codex,gemini\n```\n\n### 主动发现工作\n```bash\n# 扫描所有\n./.clawdbot/scripts/discover-work.sh all\n\n# 只扫描错误\n./.clawdbot/scripts/discover-work.sh errors\n```\n\n## 🤖 Agent选择指南\n\n| 任务类型 | 推荐Agent | 原因 |\n|---------|----------|------|\n| 后端逻辑 | Codex | 推理能力强 |\n| Bug修复 | Codex | 边界情况处理最好 |\n| 重构 | Codex | 多文件推理 |\n| 前端UI | Claude Code | 速度快 |\n| Git操作 | Claude Code | 权限问题少 |\n| 设计 | Gemini | 设计感强 |\n\n## ✅ Definition of Done\n\n- [ ] PR已创建\n- [ ] 分支与main同步（无冲突）\n- [ ] CI全部通过\n- [ ] 所有代码审查通过（Codex + Gemini）\n- [ ] UI变更附带截图\n\n## 🔄 Ralph Loop V2\n\n失败处理策略：\n- **上下文溢出** → 缩小范围，只关注核心文件\n- **方向错误** → 纠正方向，附上会议原话\n- **需要澄清** → 提供客户邮箱和背景信息\n- **CI失败** → 分析错误，生成修复指令\n- **审查失败** → 提取关键反馈，生成修改指令\n\n## 📊 定时任务建议\n\n```bash\n# 每10分钟监控Agent\n*/10 * * * * ~/.openclaw/workspace-tech-lead/.clawdbot/scripts/check-agents.sh\n\n# 每小时发现工作\n0 * * * * ~/.openclaw/workspace-tech-lead/.clawdbot/scripts/discover-work.sh all\n\n# 每天清理完成的worktree\n0 18 * * * git worktree prune\n```","file_path":"/Users/lihzz/.openclaw/workspace-tech-lead/.clawdbot/README.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-3a6174ca5f304b0f97e8ccd0451a53c0","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"{\n  \"version\": \"1.0\",\n  \"owner\": \"Alex (技术总监)\",\n  \"description\": \"编排层 Agent 的业务上下文记忆\",\n  \"context\": {\n    \"company\": {\n      \"name\": \"OpenClaw Company\",\n      \"type\": \"AI产品公司\",\n      \"focus\": \"技术孵化、产品开发\",\n      \"github\": {\n        \"account\": \"zhushuyuan0601\",\n        \"mainRepo\": \"openclawCompany\"\n      }\n    },\n    \"team\": {\n      \"ceo\": {\n        \"name\": \"Zoe\",\n        \"agentId\": \"ceo\",\n        \"role\": \"总助理 - 统筹全局、任务调度\"\n      },\n      \"pm\": {\n        \"name\": \"Sarah\",\n        \"agentId\": \"pm\",\n        \"role\": \"产品经理 - 产品需求、PRD生成\"\n      },\n      \"researcher\": {\n        \"name\": \"情报研究员\",\n        \"agentId\": \"researcher\",\n        \"role\": \"数据采集、热点发现\"\n      },\n      \"techLead\": {\n        \"name\": \"Alex\",\n        \"agentId\": \"tech-lead\",\n        \"role\": \"技术总监 - 技术评估、Agent编排\"\n      }\n    },\n    \"projects\": [],\n    \"customers\": [],\n    \"decisions\": []\n  },\n  \"experience\": {\n    \"successfulPatterns\": [],\n    \"failedPatterns\": [],\n    \"agentPreferences\": {\n      \"codex\": \"适合90%的后端任务，边界情况处理最好\",\n      \"claude-code\": \"前端更快，Git操作权限问题少\",\n      \"gemini\": \"设计感强，先生成设计再实现\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"metadata\": {\n    \"createdAt\": \"2026-03-05T10:01:00+08:00\",\n    \"lastUpdated\": \"2026-03-05T10:01:00+08:00\"\n  }\n}","file_path":"/Users/lihzz/.openclaw/workspace-tech-lead/.clawdbot/memory/business-context.json"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-4c3594e4d70e4e1eb92de6f1d729daae","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mkdir -p ~/.openclaw/workspace-tech-lead/.clawdbot/memory ~/.openclaw/workspace-tech-lead/.clawdbot/logs ~/.openclaw/workspace-tech-lead/.clawdbot/completed-tasks"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"alibaba","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":41620,"output":1595,"cacheRead":1151,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44366,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772677633957}}
{"type":"message","id":"a7bd36a1","parentId":"fa7a1dac","timestamp":"2026-03-05T02:28:31.317Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-5087fe8c99184e1ab9fe52458001a226","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"total 88\ndrwx------  8 lihzz  staff   256 Mar  5 10:11 .\ndrwx------  8 lihzz  staff   256 Mar  5 10:07 ..\n-rwx------  1 lihzz  staff  4017 Mar  5 10:02 check-agents.sh\n-rwx------  1 lihzz  staff  6951 Mar  5 10:11 check-dod.sh\n-rwx------  1 lihzz  staff  7391 Mar  5 10:07 discover-work.sh\n-rwx------  1 lihzz  staff  9128 Mar  5 10:04 ralph-loop.sh\n-rwx------  1 lihzz  staff  3900 Mar  5 10:04 select-agent.sh\n-rwx------  1 lihzz  staff  7797 Mar  5 10:11 spawn-agent.sh"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":24,"aggregated":"total 88\ndrwx------  8 lihzz  staff   256 Mar  5 10:11 .\ndrwx------  8 lihzz  staff   256 Mar  5 10:07 ..\n-rwx------  1 lihzz  staff  4017 Mar  5 10:02 check-agents.sh\n-rwx------  1 lihzz  staff  6951 Mar  5 10:11 check-dod.sh\n-rwx------  1 lihzz  staff  7391 Mar  5 10:07 discover-work.sh\n-rwx------  1 lihzz  staff  9128 Mar  5 10:04 ralph-loop.sh\n-rwx------  1 lihzz  staff  3900 Mar  5 10:04 select-agent.sh\n-rwx------  1 lihzz  staff  7797 Mar  5 10:11 spawn-agent.sh","cwd":"/Users/lihzz/.openclaw/workspace-tech-lead"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772677711308}}
