{"type":"message","id":"43cb721c","parentId":"36dc9177","timestamp":"2026-03-05T02:32:28.010Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me update AGENTS.md to reference the new system and create a quick start guide.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-d16a939a85f341a7a917ce89e89d7747","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/lihzz/.openclaw/workspace-tech-lead/AGENTS.md","oldText":"### 调度方式\n\n**方法1：使用 sessions_spawn（推荐）**\n```bash\nsessions_spawn \\\n  --runtime acp \\\n  --task \"详细的任务描述，包含业务上下文\" \\\n  --workspace ~/.openclaw/workspace-projects/project-name\n```\n\n**方法2：使用 coding-agent skill**\n```\n使用 coding-agent skill\n任务：实现XXX功能\n技术栈：Python + FastAPI\n工作区：~/.openclaw/workspace-projects/project-name\n```\n\n### Prompt 生成模板","newText":"### 调度方式\n\n**方法1：使用 spawn-agent.sh（推荐）**\n```bash\n# 生成编码Agent\n./.clawdbot/scripts/spawn-agent.sh backend \"实现用户登录\" ~/projects/myapp myapp\n\n# 带业务上下文\n./.clawdbot/scripts/spawn-agent.sh backend \"实现SSO登录\" ~/projects/myapp myapp \\\n  \"客户需要企业SSO，支持SAML和OAuth\" \\\n  \"使用FastAPI + Authlib，PostgreSQL存储\"\n```\n\n**方法2：使用 sessions_spawn**\n```bash\nsessions_spawn \\\n  --runtime acp \\\n  --task \"详细的任务描述，包含业务上下文\" \\\n  --workspace ~/.openclaw/workspace-projects/project-name\n```\n\n**方法3：使用 coding-agent skill**\n```\n使用 coding-agent skill\n任务：实现XXX功能\n技术栈：Python + FastAPI\n工作区：~/.openclaw/workspace-projects/project-name\n```\n\n### Prompt 生成模板"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-ed6f2d55b23a49a0b85f262d99a80d89","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/lihzz/.openclaw/workspace-tech-lead/AGENTS.md","oldText":"## 💡 关键改进点\n\n### 与传统模式的区别\n\n| 传统模式 | Agent Swarm模式 |\n|---------|-----------------|\n| 我直接写代码 | 我生成prompt，Agent写代码 |\n| 线性执行 | 并行多Agent |\n| 失败就重试 | 失败分析原因，调整策略 |\n| 等待需求 | 主动发现工作 |\n| 单一上下文 | 业务上下文与代码上下文分离 |\n\n### 预期效果\n\n- **日均提交量**：从个位数提升到50+\n- **开发效率**：一人当一支团队\n- **代码质量**：多模型审查，减少bug\n- **响应速度**：需求到上线当天完成","newText":"## 📁 .clawdbot 系统\n\nAgent Swarm 编排系统已部署在 `.clawdbot/` 目录：\n\n```\n.clawdbot/\n├── active-tasks.json        # 活跃任务队列\n├── scripts/                 # 核心脚本\n│   ├── spawn-agent.sh       # 🚀 Agent生成器\n│   ├── check-agents.sh      # 📊 监控脚本\n│   ├── check-dod.sh         # ✅ DoD检查\n│   ├── ralph-loop.sh        # 🔄 智能失败处理\n│   ├── discover-work.sh     # 🔍 主动工作发现\n│   ├── generate-prompt.sh   # 📝 Prompt生成\n│   ├── select-agent.sh      # 🤖 Agent选择\n│   └── generate-report.sh   # 📈 报告生成\n├── templates/               # Prompt模板\n├── memory/                  # 经验积累\n└── logs/                    # 日志\n```\n\n### 快速开始\n\n```bash\n# 1. 生成编码Agent\n./.clawdbot/scripts/spawn-agent.sh backend \"实现用户登录\" ~/projects/myapp myapp\n\n# 2. 监控Agent状态\n./.clawdbot/scripts/check-agents.sh\n\n# 3. 检查DoD\n./.clawdbot/scripts/check-dod.sh feat/login owner/repo\n\n# 4. 生成报告\n./.clawdbot/scripts/generate-report.sh daily\n```\n\n## 💡 关键改进点\n\n### 与传统模式的区别\n\n| 传统模式 | Agent Swarm模式 |\n|---------|-----------------|\n| 我直接写代码 | 我生成prompt，Agent写代码 |\n| 线性执行 | 并行多Agent |\n| 失败就重试 | 失败分析原因，调整策略 |\n| 等待需求 | 主动发现工作 |\n| 单一上下文 | 业务上下文与代码上下文分离 |\n\n### 预期效果\n\n- **日均提交量**：从个位数提升到50+\n- **开发效率**：一人当一支团队\n- **代码质量**：多模型审查，减少bug\n- **响应速度**：需求到上线当天完成"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-c6f097a3599f495896a476a2d326c943","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"chmod +x ~/.openclaw/workspace-tech-lead/.clawdbot/scripts/*.sh && ls -la ~/.openclaw/workspace-tech-lead/.clawdbot/"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"alibaba","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":46914,"output":1128,"cacheRead":1151,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49193,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772677887010}}
