 确保选择器匹配当前网站结构\n\n4. **测试爬取功能**\n   - 运行爬虫测试\n   - 验证是否能爬取到文章\n   - 检查数据格式是否正确\n\n## 验收标准\n\n- [ ] 机器之心爬虫能爬取至少10篇文章\n- [ ] 36氪爬虫能爬取至少10篇文章\n- [ ] 新智元爬虫能爬取至少10篇文章\n- [ ] 文章数据包含标题、URL、发布时间、摘要\n- [ ] 数据成功存入SQLite数据库\n\n## 注意事项\n\n- 使用Playwright动态渲染\n- 随机延迟2-5秒避免反爬\n- 正确处理网络错误\n- 日志记录关键步骤\n\n## 测试命令\n\n```bash\ncd ~/openclawCompany/projects/ai-intel-system\npython -c \"from src.crawler.crawler_factory import CrawlerFactory; factory = CrawlerFactory(); crawlers = factory.get_enabled_crawlers(); print(f'已启用 {len(crawlers)} 个爬虫')\"\n```","cwd":"/Users/lihzz/openclawCompany/projects/ai-intel-system"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"alibaba","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":404,"output":1565,"cacheRead":71423,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73392,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772679044953}}
