{"type":"message","id":"2ce04948","parentId":"db2e2007","timestamp":"2026-03-05T02:57:33.566Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我已经修复了36氪爬虫的选择器。现在让我测试一下是否能正常工作，然后继续启动Agent Swarm模式完成剩余任务。\n\n用户要求24小时持续开发直到需求完成，所以我需要：\n1. 测试修复后的爬虫\n2. 启动编码Agent完成剩余任务\n3. 持续监控和优化\n\n让我先测试爬虫是否工作。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的！现在让我测试修复后的爬虫，并创建完整的测试验证脚本："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-97f3d15136304d0db97b8353ac5eb1cd","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\n爬虫快速测试脚本\n\"\"\"\nimport asyncio\nimport sys\nsys.path.insert(0, '/Users/lihzz/openclawCompany/projects/ai-intel-system')\n\nfrom src.crawler.kr36_crawler import Kr36Crawler\n\nasync def test_kr36():\n    \"\"\"测试36氪爬虫\"\"\"\n    print(\"🔍 测试36氪爬虫...\")\n    \n    crawler = Kr36Crawler()\n    \n    try:\n        articles = await crawler.crawl(limit=5)\n        \n        print(f\"\\n✅ 成功爬取 {len(articles)} 篇文章\\n\")\n        \n        for i, article in enumerate(articles, 1):\n            print(f\"{i}. {article.title[:50]}...\")\n            print(f\"   URL: {article.url}\")\n            print(f\"   时间: {article.published_at}\")\n            print(f\"   来源: {article.source}\")\n            print()\n            \n        return True\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"❌ 测试失败: {e}\")\n        import traceback\n        traceback.print_exc()\n        return False\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    result = asyncio.run(test_kr36())\n    sys.exit(0 if result else 1)","file_path":"/Users/lihzz/openclawCompany/projects/ai-intel-system/quick_crawl_test.py"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-b334a25577d34d56a3a2ac2c937805e8","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/openclawCompany/projects/ai-intel-system && python3 quick_crawl_test.py 2>&1 | head -50","timeout":60}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"alibaba","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":2579,"output":521,"cacheRead":106303,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":109403,"cost":