{"type":"message","id":"c83e4a13","parentId":"5f6671b4","timestamp":"2026-03-05T03:15:51.173Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户让我使用Agent Swarm模式进行24小时持续开发。我已经：\n\n1. ✅ 部署了Agent Swarm编排系统\n2. ✅ 修复了36氪爬虫，测试通过\n3. 🔄 正在继续开发\n\n现在需要：\n1. 继续修复其他爬虫（机器之心、新智元）\n2. 设置定时同步机制\n3. 持续推进直到完成所有任务\n\n让我继续推进开发，并确保定时同步状态。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的！继续推进 **Agent Swarm 24小时持续开发模式**！\n\n## 🚀 当前状态同步\n\n**✅ Task-001 完成**: 36氪爬虫修复成功！成功爬取5篇文章\n\n**🔄 Task-002 进行中**: 修复机器之心和新智元爬虫\n\n让我继续修复其他爬虫：</think>好的！收到！我会每30分钟或完成关键任务时同步状态。继续推进开发！"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-0080f9e770c54d56b1ce903cc0ec68ab","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/lihzz/openclawCompany/projects/ai-intel-system/src/crawler/jiqizhixin_crawler.py","newText":"def parse_article_list(self, html: str) -> List[Dict[str, Any]]:\n        \"\"\"解析文章列表页\"\"\"\n        articles = []\n        soup = BeautifulSoup(html, 'lxml')\n\n        # 机器之心实际结构：查找所有文章链接\n        article_items = soup.find_all('a', href=lambda x: x and '/article/' in str(x))\n\n        if not article_items:\n            logger.warning(\"未找到文章列表，尝试其他选择器...\")\n            article_items = soup.find_all('a', href=lambda x: x and '/news/' in str(x))\n\n        logger.info(f\"找到 {len(article_items)} 个文章链接\")\n\n        for item in article_items:\n            try:\n                # 标题直接在链接文本中\n                title = item.get_text(strip=True)\n                \n                if not title or len(title) < 5:\n                    continue\n\n                # 提取链接\n                url = item.get('href', '')\n                if url.startswith('/'):\n                    url = self.base_url + url\n                elif not url.startswith('http'):\n                    url = self.base_url + '/' + url\n\n                # 提取时间\n                published_at = None\n                parent = item.parent\n                if parent:\n                    time_text = parent.get_text()\n                    import re\n                    time_match = re.search(r'(\\d{4}[-/]\\d{1,2}[-/]\\d{1,2})', time_text)\n                    if time_match:\n                        try:\n                            published_at = datetime.strptime(time_match.group(1).replace('/', '-'), '%Y-%m-%d')\n                        except:\n                            published_at = datetime.now()\n\n                content = title\n\n                articles.append({\n                    \"title\": title,\n                    \"url\": url,\n                    \"published_at\": published_at or datetime.now(),\n                    \"content\": content\n                })\n\n            except Exception as e:\n                logger.debug(f\"解析文章元素失败: {e}\")\n                continue\n\n        logger.info(f\"成功解析 {len(articles)} 篇文章\")\n        return articles","oldText":"def parse_article_list(self, html: str) -> List[Dict[str, Any]]:\n        \"\"\"解析文章列表页\"\"\"\n        articles = []\n        soup = BeautifulSoup(html, 'lxml')\n\n        # 机器之心的文章列表结构\n        # 根据实际网页结构调整选择器\n        article_items = soup.select('.article-item, .article-card, article[itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Article\"]')\n\n        if not article_items:\n            logger.warning(\"未找到文章列表，尝试其他选择器...\")\n            # 尝试其他可能的选择器\n            article_items = soup.find_all('a', href=lambda x: x and x.startswith('/article'))\n\n        logger.info(f\"找到 {len(article_items)} 个文章元素\")\n\n        for item in article_items:\n            try:\n                # 提取标题\n                title_elem = item.select_one('h2, h3, .title, .article-title')\n                if not title_elem:\n                    # 尝试直接从 a 标签提取\n                    link_elem = item.select_one('a[href]')\n                    if link_elem:\n                        title_elem = link_elem\n\n                if title_elem:\n                    title = title_elem.get_text(strip=True)\n                else:\n                    continue\n\n                # 提取链接\n                link_elem = item.select_one('a[href]') or title_elem\n                if not link_elem:\n                    continue\n\n                url = link_elem.get('href', '')\n                if url.startswith('/'):\n                    url = self.base_url + url\n\n                # 提取时间\n                time_elem = item.select_one('.time, .date, .article-time, time')\n                published_at = None\n                if time_elem:\n                    time_text = time_elem.get_text(strip=True)\n                    published_at = self.parse_datetime(time_text)\n\n                # 简单的摘要\n                summary_elem = item.select_one('.summary, .excerpt, .description')\n                content = summary_elem.get_text(strip=True) if summary_elem else title\n\n                articles.append({\n                    \"title\": title,\n                    \"url\": url,\n                    \"published_at\": published_at,\n                    \"content\": content\n                })\n\n            except Exception as e:\n                logger.debug(f\"解析文章元素失败: {e}\")\n                continue\n\n        return articles"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-83bcf014449340f3827fb289cbfe3f51","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/lihzz/openclawCompany/projects/ai-intel-system/src/crawler/xinzhixing_crawler.py","newText":"def parse_article_list(self, html: str) -> List[Dict[str, Any]]:\n        \"\"\"解析文章列表页\"\"\"\n        articles = []\n        soup = BeautifulSoup(html, 'lxml')\n\n        # 新智元实际结构：查找所有文章链接\n        article_items = soup.find_all('a', href=lambda x: x and ('/article/' in str(x) or '/post/' in str(x)))\n\n        if not article_items:\n            logger.warning(\"未找到文章列表，尝试其他选择器...\")\n            article_items = soup.find_all('a', href=lambda x: x and '/news/' in str(x))\n\n        logger.info(f\"找到 {len(article_items)} 个文章链接\")\n\n        for item in article_items:\n            try:\n                # 标题直接在链接文本中\n                title = item.get_text(strip=True)\n                \n                if not title or len(title) < 5:\n                    continue\n\n                # 提取链接\n                url = item.get('href', '')\n                if url.startswith('/'):\n                    url = self.base_url + url\n                elif not url.startswith('http'):\n                    url = self.base_url + '/' + url\n\n                # 提取时间\n                published_at = None\n                parent = item.parent\n                if parent:\n                    time_text = parent.get_text()\n                    import re\n                    time_match = re.search(r'(\\d{4}[-/]\\d{1,2}[-/]\\d{1,2})', time_text)\n                    if time_match:\n                        try:\n                            published_at = datetime.strptime(time_match.group(1).replace('/', '-'), '%Y-%m-%d')\n                        except:\n                            published_at = datetime.now()\n\n                content = title\n\n                articles.append({\n                    \"title\": title,\n                    \"url\": url,\n                    \"published_at\": published_at or datetime.now(),\n                    \"content\": content\n                })\n\n            except Exception as e:\n                logger.debug(f\"解析文章元素失败: {e}\")\n                continue\n\n        logger.info(f\"成功解析 {len(articles)} 篇文章\")\n        return articles","oldText":"def parse_article_list(self, html: str) -> List[Dict[str, Any]]:\n        \"\"\"解析文章列表页\"\"\"\n        articles = []\n        soup = BeautifulSoup(html, 'lxml')\n\n        # 新智元的文章列表结构\n        article_items = soup.select('.article-item, .article-card, article')\n\n        if not article_items:\n            logger.warning(\"未找到文章列表，尝试其他选择器...\")\n            article_items = soup.find_all('a', href=lambda x: x and '/article' in str(x))\n\n        logger.info(f\"找到 {len(article_items)} 个文章元素\")\n\n        for item in article_items:\n            try:\n                # 提取标题\n                title_elem = item.select_one('h2, h3, .title, .article-title')\n                if not title_elem:\n                    link_elem = item.select_one('a[href]')\n                    if link_elem:\n                        title_elem = link_elem\n\n                if title_elem:\n                    title = title_elem.get_text(strip=True)\n                else:\n                    continue\n\n                # 提取链接\n                link_elem = item.select_one('a[href]') or title_elem\n                if not link_elem:\n                    continue\n\n                url = link_elem.get('href', '')\n                if url.startswith('/'):\n                    url = self.base_url + url\n                elif not url.startswith('http'):\n                    url = self.base_url + '/' + url\n\n                # 提取时间\n                time_elem = item.select_one('.time, .date, .article-time, time')\n                published_at = None\n                if time_elem:\n                    time_text = time_elem.get_text(strip=True)\n                    published_at = self.parse_datetime(time_text)\n\n                # 摘要\n                summary_elem = item.select_one('.summary, .description, .excerpt')\n                content = summary_elem.get_text(strip=True) if summary_elem else title\n\n                articles.append({\n                    \"title\": title,\n                    \"url\": url,\n                    \"published_at\": published_at,\n                    \"content\": content\n                })\n\n            except Exception as e:\n                logger.debug(f\"解析文章元素失败: {e}\")\n                continue\n\n        return articles"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-d0da26d10db84c779e950a37aba90cc1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\n所有爬虫批量测试脚本\n\"\"\"\nimport asyncio\nimport sys\nsys.path.insert(0, '/Users/lihzz/openclawCompany/projects/ai-intel-system')\n\nfrom src.crawler.crawler_factory import CrawlerFactory\n\nasync def test_all_crawlers():\n    \"\"\"测试所有启用的爬虫\"\"\"\n    print(\"=\" * 60)\n    print(\"🚀 批量测试所有爬虫\")\n    print(\"=\" * 60)\n    \n    factory = CrawlerFactory()\n    crawlers = factory.get_enabled_crawlers()\n    \n    print(f\"\\n📊 已启用 {len(crawlers)} 个爬虫:\")\n    for c in crawlers:\n        print(f\"   - {c.source_name}\")\n    print()\n    \n    all_results = {}\n    \n    for crawler in crawlers:\n        print(f\"\\n{'='*60}\")\n        print(f\"🔍 测试 {crawler.source_name} 爬虫...\")\n        print(f\"{'='*60}\")\n        \n        try:\n            articles = await crawler.crawl(limit=3)\n            \n            if articles:\n                print(f\"\\n✅ 成功爬取 {len(articles)} 篇文章\")\n                print()\n                for i, article in enumerate(articles, 1):\n                    print(f\"{i}. {article.title[:60]}...\")\n                    print(f\"   URL: {article.url}\")\n                    print(f\"   时间: {article.published_at}\")\n                    print()\n                all_results[crawler.source_name] = len(articles)\n            else:\n                print(f\"\\n⚠️  未爬取到文章\")\n                all_results[crawler.source_name] = 0\n                \n        except Exception as e:\n            print(f\"\\n❌ 测试失败: {e}\")\n            all_results[crawler.source_name] = -1\n            import traceback\n            traceback.print_exc()\n    \n    # 汇总结果\n    print(\"\\n\" + \"=\" * 60)\n    print(\"📊 测试汇总\")\n    print(\"=\" * 60)\n    \n    total = 0\n    for source, count in all_results.items():\n        status = \"✅\" if count > 0 else \"❌\" if count < 0 else \"⚠️\"\n        print(f\"{status} {source}: {count if count >= 0 else '失败'}\")\n        if count > 0:\n            total += count\n    \n    print(f\"\\n总计: 成功爬取 {total} 篇文章\")\n    print(\"=\" * 60)\n    \n    return total > 0\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    result = asyncio.run(test_all_crawlers())\n    sys.exit(0 if result else 1)","file_path":"/Users/lihzz/openclawCompany/projects/ai-intel-system/test_all_crawlers.py"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-baeb7c626c2141e998e28253867edaf9","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/openclawCompany/projects/ai-intel-system && python3 test_all_crawlers.py 2>&1","timeout":180}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"alibaba","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":948,"output":2788,"cacheRead":111039,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":114775,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772680418638}}
